{
  "stem": "5799.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And somehow I became-- it was a paradox-- that although I did not believe exactly in God, I started to believe that-- although I am a fatalist-- it will be, whatever it'll be-- but God helps those who help themselves-- and looking for a way out.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While I was in the ghetto, I saw people smuggling in through the-- at night, after curfew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't finished yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The barbed wire wasn't put down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The fence wasn't finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very primitive yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would talk to them and hide them in the attic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I never told my parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never told my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because if I would tell them, I think they would give it out first thing to the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They would think that I am jeopardizing the life of the whole ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And while I worked on the cemetery, there was an old German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He must have been around 40.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] It shows how you think when you are 17, that 40 is old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He told me he is a farmer and that he had two children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He would bring us bread-- not the others, but me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I would share it-- give each one a slice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And walking once to work, I saw a sign-- a bandit by then-- a Jew-- by the name of Tuvia Bielski is given for his head any information-- so many, and so many.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember how many-- how many-- the German money-- some-- some-- some-- some kind of a ridiculous sum it was.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I said, by golly, to this Jew I'm going to go-- but how?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who-- You saw a sign?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A, you know--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--on the kiosk-- a wanted sign.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw Jew-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
